    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "KILLABEATMAKER | The Feeling of Free | Jul 7 - 9, 2026 | Wood Terrace"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40964/killabeatmaker_pic_4__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "El español sigue al texto en inglés\n\nSpend your night with us taking in the sunset and vibing to music! Access our terrace directly from Elgin Street, the canal, or the Mackenzie King Bridge and take in the best free beats offered in Ottawa this summer. \n\nKillabeatmaker combines Colombian rhythms with Afrobeats, Amapiano and Cumbia. \n\nThe show brings a grooving and mystical combination through an energetic performance with unique instruments from their motherland. \n\nThe live band is made up of three musicians Guadalupe Giraldo..."
      }
    ],
